author: Paulyn Abando
title: Hi, Athalia!
text:
by Paulyn Abando
October 2, 2015 Empress Schuck and Athalia (photo from the actress’ Instagram)
Empress Schuck has given birth to Athalia, her baby girl with non-showbiz boyfriend Vino Guingona, who was present during the delivery.
The actress’ co-manager Katrina Aguila posted on Instagram a photo of Empress in labor but was still able to do the “pabebe wave.”
Vino is the nephew of Sen. Teofisto Guingona III and the grandson of former Vice President Teofisto Guingona Jr.
Empress’ shows in the past include “Super Inggo,” “Apoy Sa Dagat,” “Lastikman,” “100 Days To Heaven” and “Kailan Ba Tama Ang Mali?”
